 * HapticServer.cpp  –  Master Side  (v5: Experiment Capture Modes)
 * ============================================================================
 * ORIGINAL v4 features preserved.
 *
 * NEW in v5  –  Experiment Keys
 * ─────────────────────────────
 *  Press  1   → Experiment A: capture 1000 pkts at 1000 Hz, NO added delay.
 *               Saves: experiment_nodelay.csv
 *  Press  2   → Experiment B: capture 100 pkts, constant 250 ms system delay.
 *               Saves: experiment_const250.csv
 *  Press  3   → Experiment C: capture 100 pkts, random delay U[250,500] ms.
 *               Saves: experiment_rand250_500.csv
 *
 *  Each CSV row:
 *    index, tx_timestamp_ms, rx_timestamp_ms, delay_ms,
 *    tx_x, tx_y, tx_z, rx_x, rx_y, rx_z
 *
 *  While an experiment is running, all haptic behaviour is unchanged;
 *  the experiment simply tags outgoing packets and records when their
 *  matching reply arrives back.
 *
 * All original keys remain:
 *  T/R/F   TX | RX | FB toggle
 *  E / P   EBA | Projection toggle
 *  X/Y/Z   axis mask
 *  D       toggle delay injection ON/OFF
 *  ,  .    constant delay  −5 ms / +5 ms   (0 … 500 ms)
 *  N  M    random jitter   −5 ms / +5 ms   (0 … 200 ms)
 *  +/-     candle window    [  ]  preset    ESC quit
 *
 * *** SET CLIENT_IP ***
 */

